OL,4,CDr Michael Heath: Families feared they
OL,5,Ccremated the wrong person
OL,6, Two bereaved families feared they had
OL,7, "cremated the wrong person" due to
OL,8, errors in the post-mortem reports of a
OL,9, serially discredited pathologist.
OL,11,FThe BBC has spoken to several families
OL,12,Fwho say Dr Michael Heath made multiple
OL,13,Ferrors in his investigations into the
OL,14,Fdeaths of their loved ones.
OL,16,FHe led a disputed forensic inquiry into
OL,17,Fthe death of Stuart Lubbock after a
OL,18,Fparty at Michael Barrymore's home.
OL,20,FDr Heath's work also led to a man being
OL,21,Fwrongly convicted of murder.
